<!-- SLIDE 5 -->
<div class="slide" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552820728-8b83bb6b773f')">
    <div class="panel">
        🖥️ PC GAMING

        Discover exciting PC games and connect with fellow players.

        Explore multiplayer adventures, competitive experiences, strategy games, simulations, role-playing games, and more.
